cat << EOF
Haskell-Source with Extensions (HSE, haskell-src-exts) is a standalone parser
for Haskell. In addition to standard Haskell, all extensions implemented in
GHC are supported.

Apart from these standard extensions, it also handles regular patterns as
per the HaRP extension as well as HSX-style embedded XML syntax.
EOF
